00:36:12,680 --> 00:36:15,710
Mom. I think Jung Hee went deaf.

573
00:37:02,460 --> 00:37:05,160
Oh no! Why didn't it go off?

574
00:37:07,600 --> 00:37:09,520
You're up.

575
00:37:09,660 --> 00:37:12,160
The alarms went off, but
you wouldn't wake up.

576
00:37:12,160 --> 00:37:15,000
You should've woken me!

577
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:21,100
Don't just go. Eat something first.

578
00:37:21,210 --> 00:37:23,180
No. I have no time.

579
00:37:23,180 --> 00:37:25,540
I mixed it with an egg and sesame oil.

580
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:28,450
Okay. Bye.

581
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:30,350
Jung Hee.

582
00:37:31,120 --> 00:37:33,350
She didn't even eat.

583
00:37:34,230 --> 00:37:35,430
Out of my way!

584
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:45,140
They say co-ed rooms fill up quickly.

585
00:37:56,640 --> 00:38:01,350
(Spies don't wear signs.
We should all look.)

586
00:38:06,210 --> 00:38:07,350
Co-ed?

587
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,830
That's strange. Co-ed?

588
00:38:18,370 --> 00:38:21,310
I want a white one. I want the co-ed room.

589
00:38:21,310 --> 00:38:22,430
It's full.

590
00:38:23,040 --> 00:38:24,210
No.

591
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:32,120
Dong Moon? Dong Moon!

592
00:38:32,250 --> 00:38:33,520
Dong Moon!

593
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:36,850
Jung Hee.

594
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:41,520
Come on. Trade with me.

595
00:38:43,180 --> 00:38:46,060
That's for the girl's room.

596
00:38:46,230 --> 00:38:47,500
Then...

597
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:51,370
can't you give me that and get a new one?

598
00:38:51,930 --> 00:38:55,430
The boys' room will be filled by now.

599
00:38:57,540 --> 00:38:59,100
If I give this to you,

600
00:38:59,100 --> 00:39:01,040
I have to wait until someone leaves.

601
00:39:01,410 --> 00:39:03,680
Dong Moon. Please?

602
00:39:03,770 --> 00:39:06,520
Come on, Dong Moon.

603
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,580
Please?

604
00:39:17,460 --> 00:39:19,730
- Thanks.
- Wait.

605
00:39:20,060 --> 00:39:21,500
Jung Hee...

606
00:39:30,600 --> 00:39:32,910
(Co-ed Room)

607
00:40:20,750 --> 00:40:22,250
Son Jin.

608
00:40:23,230 --> 00:40:24,830
Jin.

609
00:40:40,040 --> 00:40:42,350
Hi, Jin.

610
00:40:43,310 --> 00:40:45,450
Do you remember me?

611
00:40:48,210 --> 00:40:49,210
No.

612
00:40:52,660 --> 00:40:55,250
The Culture Night...

613
00:40:55,980 --> 00:40:58,390
No. That's not right.

614
00:41:02,120 --> 00:41:05,600
Anyway, this is a chance of a lifetime.

615
00:41:07,310 --> 00:41:08,770
Don't shy away from it.

616
00:41:27,020 --> 00:41:28,430
Hello.

617
00:41:30,750 --> 00:41:33,020
Last time, at Culture Night...

618
00:41:35,000 --> 00:41:36,100
Why are you...

619
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:41,210
Why are you here?

620
00:41:44,080 --> 00:41:46,410
Jin, who was sitting here, just left.

621
00:41:46,410 --> 00:41:47,500
What?

622
00:41:52,450 --> 00:41:54,450
Jung Hee.

623
00:42:13,810 --> 00:42:16,640
- Jung Hee.
- You'll get hurt! Move!

624
00:42:18,870 --> 00:42:21,000
Jung Hee. Where are you going?

625
00:43:43,020 --> 00:43:44,560
Ouch.

626
00:43:55,540 --> 00:43:56,600
Are you okay?

627
00:44:01,210 --> 00:44:02,310
Are you hurt?

628
00:44:02,980 --> 00:44:04,020
Let me see.

629
00:44:06,410 --> 00:44:08,980
Oh no. Can you stand?

630
00:44:34,350 --> 00:44:35,910
You're all cut up.

631
00:44:46,180 --> 00:44:47,230
Are you okay?

632
00:44:50,850 --> 00:44:52,000
Excuse me.

633
00:44:52,520 --> 00:44:53,770
Are you okay?

634
00:44:55,620 --> 00:44:57,200
Are you badly hurt?

635
00:44:57,500 --> 00:44:58,700
That very moment,

636
00:44:58,830 --> 00:45:02,210
something made me feel very nervous.

637
00:45:02,810 --> 00:45:03,810
What is this?

638
00:45:03,810 --> 00:45:05,370
Are you okay?

639
00:45:07,040 --> 00:45:09,140
Are you okay?

640
00:45:10,100 --> 00:45:11,450
You're hurt badly.

641
00:45:11,450 --> 00:45:12,850
Let's go to the doctor.

642
00:45:13,210 --> 00:45:15,640
No, I'm fine.

643
00:45:15,680 --> 00:45:16,790
But you're bleeding.

644
00:45:16,790 --> 00:45:19,310
I'm fine. I'll just go to the pharmacy.

645
00:45:19,310 --> 00:45:22,250
Sorry, but we were in
the middle of moving...

646
00:45:22,250 --> 00:45:24,830
Hae Joo. You should help her.

647
00:45:25,290 --> 00:45:26,350
Okay, Dad.

648
00:45:26,350 --> 00:45:28,000
Thanks.

649
00:45:30,460 --> 00:45:31,830
Can you walk?

650
00:45:34,210 --> 00:45:35,210
Get on.

651
00:45:38,270 --> 00:45:39,600
I said to get on.

652
00:45:47,410 --> 00:45:49,540
I'm dreaming.

653
00:45:49,540 --> 00:45:51,060
I'm still dreaming.

654
00:45:51,290 --> 00:45:54,080
If it's a dream, please don't wake up.

655
00:45:54,680 --> 00:45:56,250
Does it hurt that badly?

656
00:46:02,520 --> 00:46:05,430
Is this really happening?

657
00:46:08,100 --> 00:46:10,830
I can die happy now.

658
00:46:12,040 --> 00:46:14,600
She must be in a lot of pain. Oh no.

659
00:46:18,520 --> 00:46:20,580
Look. There's a pharmacy.

660
00:46:21,140 --> 00:46:22,140
Okay.

661
00:46:22,350 --> 00:46:23,560
It's open.

662
00:46:25,410 --> 00:46:27,890
(Kim's Pharmacy)

663
00:46:30,060 --> 00:46:34,000
That stupid. Why is it open on a Sunday?

664
00:46:38,270 --> 00:46:39,600
Go somewhere else.

665
00:46:40,100 --> 00:46:41,660
We're not open for business today.

666
00:46:43,710 --> 00:46:45,080
I'm sorry,

667
00:46:45,080 --> 00:46:46,830
but someone fell.

668
00:46:47,270 --> 00:46:48,480
Darn it.

669
00:47:01,290 --> 00:47:02,350
You look fine.

670
00:47:03,230 --> 00:47:04,960
No, not me.

671
00:47:06,560 --> 00:47:09,230
Jung Hee. What's wrong?

672
00:47:09,930 --> 00:47:11,770
Were you hurt?

673
00:47:12,000 --> 00:47:13,710
She fell off her bike.

674
00:47:14,000 --> 00:47:15,460
We need an antiseptic...

675
00:47:15,460 --> 00:47:16,660
Sir!

676
00:47:16,980 --> 00:47:19,210
Jung Hee's hurt. Please come out.

677
00:47:19,870 --> 00:47:22,250
You ride your bike so well.

678
00:47:23,450 --> 00:47:24,680
Where was your head?

679
00:47:24,680 --> 00:47:26,270
We need to stop the bleeding.

680
00:47:26,270 --> 00:47:29,210
- Please get us...
- Ask the pharmacist.

681
00:47:29,910 --> 00:47:31,060
Sir!

682
00:47:36,850 --> 00:47:38,460
I'm sorry. It must hurt.

683
00:47:38,620 --> 00:47:40,620
Still, you have to get the dirt out.

684
00:47:41,390 --> 00:47:42,390
Let me see.

685
00:47:43,290 --> 00:47:45,430
You have so much dirt on the wound.

686
00:47:57,080 --> 00:47:59,250
Jung Hee. Let me see.

687
00:48:01,890 --> 00:48:03,410
Let me get you an antiseptic.

688
00:48:04,180 --> 00:48:07,080
Okay. I'll go work then.

689
00:48:07,080 --> 00:48:08,520
Go ahead.

690
00:48:08,930 --> 00:48:11,290
You're going to be rich, Young Choon.

691
00:48:11,520 --> 00:48:12,890
You work so hard.

692
00:48:12,890 --> 00:48:13,930
Not at all.

693
00:48:14,200 --> 00:48:15,790
Let me see.

694
00:48:17,230 --> 00:48:18,640
That hurts.

695
00:48:18,790 --> 00:48:20,140
You crybaby.

696
00:48:26,830 --> 00:48:34,850
(Kim's Pharmacy)

697
00:48:39,660 --> 00:48:41,290
Are you really okay?

698
00:48:41,790 --> 00:48:44,290
Yes, I'm fine now.

699
00:48:44,830 --> 00:48:46,790
I'll go then.

700
00:48:51,830 --> 00:48:54,140
Call me here if something else hurts...

701
00:48:54,140 --> 00:48:55,460
or anything.

702
00:48:56,410 --> 00:48:57,580
Okay?

703
00:49:00,100 --> 00:49:01,100
I will.

704
00:49:20,290 --> 00:49:21,290
I...

705
00:49:22,060 --> 00:49:23,060
Yes?

706
00:49:23,290 --> 00:49:25,600
I'm okay now.

707
00:49:26,160 --> 00:49:27,460
I can go alone.

708
00:49:29,160 --> 00:49:31,680
No, I'll walk you home.

709
00:49:42,140 --> 00:49:43,180
But...

710
00:49:43,710 --> 00:49:45,580
where were you rushing to?

711
00:49:45,960 --> 00:49:48,660
What? Well...

712
00:49:49,250 --> 00:49:51,100
Why do you go so far to study?

713
00:49:51,120 --> 00:49:52,120
What?

714
00:49:54,960 --> 00:49:56,120
You almost fell again.

715
00:49:56,120 --> 00:49:57,960
Well... I thought...

716
00:49:57,960 --> 00:50:00,640
a change of scenery...

717
00:50:00,770 --> 00:50:04,080
would help me study better.

718
00:50:05,000 --> 00:50:06,000
So?

719
00:50:06,480 --> 00:50:07,710
Did it?

720
00:50:08,000 --> 00:50:09,870
- What?
- I guess not.

721
00:50:09,870 --> 00:50:11,520
That's why you left so early.

722
00:50:12,870 --> 00:50:14,640
That's not why.

723
00:50:15,210 --> 00:50:17,310
I had an errand to run.

724
00:50:17,310 --> 00:50:19,310
What's going on here?

725
00:50:19,310 --> 00:50:20,890
You left early in the morning to study,

726
00:50:20,890 --> 00:50:22,830
and you're flirting with
a guy on the street?

727
00:50:22,830 --> 00:50:24,160
Who's this punk?

728
00:50:26,460 --> 00:50:27,520
Sir.

729
00:50:29,960 --> 00:50:32,160
Hello. Oh no.

730
00:50:33,230 --> 00:50:35,270
I attend Gaeryong High. I'm in...
Which class?

731
00:50:35,270 --> 00:50:36,730
- 11-5.
- 11-5.

732
00:50:36,730 --> 00:50:38,540
- What's my number?
- 28.

733
00:50:38,540 --> 00:50:40,950
Number 28, Lee Bong Soo.

734
00:50:41,180 --> 00:50:42,640
- Lee Bong Soo?
- Yes.

735
00:50:43,180 --> 00:50:45,080
He's my brother. Twin brother.

736
00:50:45,080 --> 00:50:46,180
I see.

737
00:50:47,040 --> 00:50:48,210
You're Bong Soo.

738
00:50:49,020 --> 00:50:50,810
- What's your name?
- I'm...

739
00:50:50,810 --> 00:50:53,980
She's Jung Hee. Lee Jung Hee. My sister.

740
00:50:54,390 --> 00:50:56,250
- Jung Hee.
- Yes.

741
00:50:56,790 --> 00:50:58,930
- Bong Soo.
- Yes, sir.

742
00:50:58,930 --> 00:51:01,890
I left your sister's bike at the bike shop.

743
00:51:03,230 --> 00:51:04,230
What?

744
00:51:04,770 --> 00:51:06,270
Your sister's hurt,

745
00:51:06,870 --> 00:51:07,910
so you go pick it up.

746
00:51:07,910 --> 00:51:08,910
What?

747
00:51:09,000 --> 00:51:11,140
Okay.

748
00:51:12,330 --> 00:51:14,370
- Jung Hee.
- Yes?

749
00:51:14,370 --> 00:51:15,370
See you again.

750
00:51:20,450 --> 00:51:22,310
Have a nice day, sir!

751
00:51:22,790 --> 00:51:23,910
Wait.

752
00:51:28,120 --> 00:51:29,390
Thank you.

753
00:51:29,730 --> 00:51:32,250
Don't chase after me so hard next time.

754
00:51:32,500 --> 00:51:33,790
You'll get hurt.

755
00:51:34,270 --> 00:51:35,890
- What?
- Get better soon.

756
00:51:47,500 --> 00:51:49,980
What's going on? Why was he with you?

757
00:51:51,210 --> 00:51:52,620
Are you chasing after him?

758
00:51:52,750 --> 00:51:54,750
You fell while chasing him, didn't you?

759
00:51:55,120 --> 00:51:56,480
Seriously!

760
00:52:00,120 --> 00:52:01,160
What the...

761
00:52:01,230 --> 00:52:03,290
Did you yell at your big brother?

762
00:52:03,430 --> 00:52:05,160
I'm telling Dad.

763
00:52:05,160 --> 00:52:06,200
Get over here!

764
00:52:07,230 --> 00:52:08,290
Hey!

765
00:52:10,790 --> 00:52:12,290
I'm right.

766
00:52:12,770 --> 00:52:15,000
You're chasing Jin too, aren't you?

767
00:52:15,000 --> 00:52:17,730
Goodness. Jung Hee. What is your problem?

768
00:52:17,730 --> 00:52:19,580
Try using that energy to study.

769
00:52:19,580 --> 00:52:21,270
Shut it.

770
00:52:21,350 --> 00:52:24,480
I guess you're all better.
You were dying earlier.

771
00:52:24,480 --> 00:52:27,310
Seriously! Just go, and get my bike.

772
00:52:27,680 --> 00:52:30,080
No. You get it yourself.

773
00:52:30,210 --> 00:52:33,660
Why you... Jin told you to get it for me!

774
00:52:33,750 --> 00:52:34,850
You said you would!

775
00:52:34,850 --> 00:52:36,830
I don't care who said what.

776
00:52:36,830 --> 00:52:39,020
Tell him to stuff it.

777
00:52:41,200 --> 00:52:43,560
What's that? Someone's moving in.

778
00:52:43,700 --> 00:52:45,200
- Where?
- There.

779
00:52:48,600 --> 00:52:50,830
Look at Young Choon.

780
00:52:51,180 --> 00:52:52,640
He's everywhere.

781
00:52:52,680 --> 00:52:55,480
He works so hard for such a pretty boy.

782
00:52:59,250 --> 00:53:00,790
Where should I put this?

783
00:53:00,890 --> 00:53:02,520
Just leave it by the door.

784
00:53:26,870 --> 00:53:29,680
Is that an angel?

785
00:53:31,520 --> 00:53:32,910
She must be human, right?

786
00:53:32,910 --> 00:53:35,040
Hey. I'm leaving.

787
00:53:35,810 --> 00:53:37,460
Why are you going that way?

788
00:53:38,290 --> 00:53:39,290
Jung Hee!

789
00:53:39,960 --> 00:53:41,080
Jung Hee!

790
00:53:41,930 --> 00:53:43,790
Wow. She's so pretty.

791
00:53:44,200 --> 00:53:45,230
Jung Hee!

792
00:53:46,060 --> 00:53:47,200
Jung Hee!

793
00:53:54,730 --> 00:53:55,960
I can do it.

794
00:53:56,730 --> 00:53:57,810
I'll take it.

795
00:54:00,040 --> 00:54:01,350
Thank you.

796
00:54:08,950 --> 00:54:11,180
Jung Hee!

797
00:54:11,660 --> 00:54:12,980
Jung Hee!

798
00:54:14,560 --> 00:54:16,330
- You're coming home now?
- You...

799
00:54:16,890 --> 00:54:18,230
know where I live?

800
00:54:18,620 --> 00:54:21,060
No. You rushed out so suddenly,

801
00:54:21,230 --> 00:54:22,870
I was worried and ran after you.

802
00:54:30,580 --> 00:54:32,980
What happened... What happened there?

803
00:54:33,330 --> 00:54:34,850
None of your business. Just go.

804
00:54:38,750 --> 00:54:39,870
But hey.

805
00:54:40,950 --> 00:54:43,660
What were you doing at Taehyang Library?

806
00:54:46,180 --> 00:54:47,750
Well, the thing is...

807
00:54:48,480 --> 00:54:50,850
I guess Gaeryong High kids go there.

808
00:54:51,060 --> 00:54:55,020
True. Son Jin, the student
body president, goes too.

809
00:54:55,500 --> 00:54:56,620
Right?

810
00:54:57,140 --> 00:54:58,960
Yes, that's right.

811
00:54:59,870 --> 00:55:02,830
What about you? Why did you go so far?

812
00:55:04,810 --> 00:55:06,640
- Dong Moon.
- Yes?

813
00:55:07,680 --> 00:55:09,770
- You...
- Yes?

814
00:55:09,810 --> 00:55:11,370
don't need to know.

815
00:55:24,330 --> 00:55:25,560
That must hurt.

816
00:55:36,560 --> 00:55:38,930
Jung Hee. Why are you home so early?

817
00:55:41,350 --> 00:55:42,540
Oh my gosh.

818
00:55:43,770 --> 00:55:46,520
Oh my gosh. Are you hurt? How?

819
00:55:46,980 --> 00:55:48,180
It's nothing.

820
00:55:52,910 --> 00:55:54,020
Oh my gosh.

821
00:56:02,870 --> 00:56:05,000
Are you okay? Are you hurt?

822
00:56:05,200 --> 00:56:06,230
Let me see.

823
00:56:06,430 --> 00:56:09,210
Oh no. Can you stand?

824
00:56:09,410 --> 00:56:10,500
Jung Hee.

825
00:56:12,370 --> 00:56:13,500
See you again.

826
00:56:20,680 --> 00:56:21,910
Yes.

827
00:56:39,200 --> 00:56:42,100
Let me see. You have so
much dirt on the wound.

828
00:56:47,680 --> 00:56:48,910
That's strange.

829
00:56:49,350 --> 00:56:51,480
I was so happy earlier.

830
00:56:51,850 --> 00:56:53,850
Why do I feel so down now?

831
00:57:02,350 --> 00:57:04,020
It's because I miss him.

832
00:57:04,290 --> 00:57:07,520
The more I think of him,
the more I miss him.

833
00:57:07,700 --> 00:57:10,560
That's why I keep feeling down.

834
00:57:15,060 --> 00:57:18,100
How can I wait until Sunday?

835
00:57:20,000 --> 00:57:21,450
Keep it down!

836
00:57:21,980 --> 00:57:23,450
Go to sleep!

837
00:57:28,180 --> 00:57:29,790
Son Jin did that?

838
00:57:34,620 --> 00:57:37,960
Do you mean it? You were on Son Jin's back?

839
00:57:38,160 --> 00:57:39,350
Really?

840
00:57:40,390 --> 00:57:41,930
You rubbed your chest...

841
00:57:42,120 --> 00:57:44,730
onto Jin's back like this?

842
00:57:44,730 --> 00:57:47,100
Come on. I didn't do that.

843
00:57:47,100 --> 00:57:48,270
What do you mean?

844
00:57:48,810 --> 00:57:52,100
How could you be on his back without...

845
00:57:52,140 --> 00:57:53,580
rubbing them on it?

846
00:57:54,640 --> 00:57:56,600
- You're terrible!
- Come on!

847
00:57:56,600 --> 00:57:57,910
Shut it!

848
00:57:58,520 --> 00:57:59,910
Keep it down!

849
00:58:02,250 --> 00:58:05,060
I'll take down all of your names.

850
00:58:08,660 --> 00:58:09,730
Be quiet.

851
00:58:10,850 --> 00:58:12,020
Study.

852
00:58:14,120 --> 00:58:16,120
- Hush.
- You brat.

853
00:58:19,390 --> 00:58:21,660
(Student Transcript)

854
00:58:41,960 --> 00:58:45,020
(It's game over.)

855
00:58:45,020 --> 00:58:47,770
It's game over.

856
00:58:49,290 --> 00:58:51,600
That's right. Jung Hee,

857
00:58:51,600 --> 00:58:53,430
