858
00:58:53,430 --> 00:58:55,430
of Daegu's hottie, Son Jin.

859
00:59:02,370 --> 00:59:05,080
It's not like that.

860
00:59:06,210 --> 00:59:07,480
It is too.

861
00:59:08,540 --> 00:59:10,250
There's a girl named Choi Duk Boon...

862
00:59:10,560 --> 00:59:12,290
from Dongsung Girls' School,

863
00:59:12,290 --> 00:59:14,620
who's infamous for following Jin around.

864
00:59:14,620 --> 00:59:18,290
She fell in front of his school one day,

865
00:59:18,500 --> 00:59:20,500
