866
00:59:20,500 --> 00:59:23,390
Do you know what he did?

867
00:59:23,830 --> 00:59:24,960
What did he do?

868
00:59:31,640 --> 00:59:34,850
- Be careful.
- And then he took off.

869
00:59:34,850 --> 00:59:37,770
She was bleeding in the
middle of the street.

870
00:59:38,020 --> 00:59:41,210
No way. I'm sure she was
not bleeding that much.

871
00:59:41,980 --> 00:59:43,250
Regardless.

872
00:59:43,580 --> 00:59:45,520
That's how he is.

873
00:59:45,910 --> 00:59:48,790
That's right. He's cold and arrogant.

874
01:00:11,250 --> 01:00:12,450
That's right.

875
01:00:12,710 --> 01:00:16,850
He's famous for not giving
girls a second look.

876
01:00:17,020 --> 01:00:18,180
But...

877
01:00:18,850 --> 01:00:21,160
