880
01:00:32,960 --> 01:00:34,230
This.

881
01:00:35,370 --> 01:00:36,460
This?

882
01:00:39,370 --> 01:00:41,270
Awesome!

883
01:00:41,770 --> 01:00:44,680
Stop that. Sit down.

884
01:00:46,750 --> 01:00:48,250
Jung Hee. Ki Ryuh!

885
01:00:50,460 --> 01:00:52,580
You brats.

886
01:00:52,810 --> 01:00:55,580
Why are you worst students in the class...

887
01:00:55,580 --> 01:00:57,890
