907
01:02:13,710 --> 01:02:16,060
Say hi to the class.

908
01:02:19,140 --> 01:02:20,350
Hello.

909
01:02:20,810 --> 01:02:23,640
I'm Park Hae Joo. I transferred from Seoul.

910
01:02:24,270 --> 01:02:26,350
- Seoul?
- Wow.

911
01:02:26,350 --> 01:02:29,020
- She's so pretty.
- She's a Seoul girl.

912
01:02:31,810 --> 01:02:33,460
How humiliating.

913
01:02:38,020 --> 01:02:39,100
What is this...

914
01:02:40,100 --> 01:02:41,730
