925
01:03:48,020 --> 01:03:49,890
Joint? With Gaeryong?

926
01:03:49,890 --> 01:03:52,500
While preparing the show, you and Jin...

927
01:03:52,500 --> 01:03:54,060
It's too soon to relax.

928
01:03:54,060 --> 01:03:56,710
That pretty Seoul girl may be an obstacle.
